---
title: Chorizo Nacho Platters with Salsa and Crema
description: A glorious Spanish-inspired nacho platter, loaded to the brim! Grab the kids, mix and match the toppings and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nachos-au-chorizo-9f4ab735.jpg
